他野雞degree或者相關科目嘅fg<br />\n<br />\n全港得space一個HA認嘅dietetics program<br />\n仲要兩年開一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59470678ad9171004055759cb2f308d8aadee709","tid":2099883,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df70347844ac56a2b2b3248e678fb7fd089d0cb9","tid":2099883,"uid":362508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"黎緊hkuspace 面試，擔心萬一收我d野完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"横掂文科轉science <br />\n不如直接轉healthcare eg 讀nursing school/aso駁bachelor of nursing<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以考慮下讀個nursing degree增值加學D醫學知識<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港讀nursing 畢業直接用香港牌排移民去澳洲的<br />\n<br />\n澳洲護士：病人比例好過香港 人工扣稅後高香港少少<br />\n<br />\n英文能力要求容易 唔想考IELTS 可以考較簡單的OET(nursing)<br />\n<br />\n有人為仔女教育<br />\n有人為住好D<br />\n有人為開心D 唔使日日聽柒婆9up<br />\n有人為工作環境多D mutual respect無咁malignant<br />\n有人為多D autonomy 做nurse practitioner<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKTFNY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKTFNY3.png&h=ac0516c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDptWSr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDptWSr.jpg&h=4a1a1ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yV3Kvcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyV3Kvcs.jpg&h=9250b4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Zfpvct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Zfpvct.jpg&h=ec0512b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲</span></strong>總理辦公室今日發出新聞稿，簡單列明了措施<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>接收香港移民</strong></span>：<br />\n<br />\n留學生簽證<br />\n<br />\n目前和將來的香港留學生，畢業時可申請5年的畢業生簽證，5年後有途徑申請永久居留權。<br />\n已畢業兼正持有畢業生簽證的人士，可申請延長畢業簽證，由今日起計加多5年，完結後有途徑申請永久居留權。<br />\n到偏遠地區校園讀書的留學生，繼續可在畢業3年後，有途徑申請永久居留權。<br />\n臨時技術簽證<br />\n<br />\n目前持有臨時技術簽證的香港人，可申請額外居留5年，之後有途徑申請永久居留權。<br />\n將來持有臨時技術簽證的港人，符合以下條件便可申請5年簽證：<br />\n──職位在技術職業清單內，並符合勞力市場測試要求；或<br />\n──合資格參加優才Global Talent臨時簽證計劃，這類簽證是給予年薪高於15萬3,600元、具出眾才能及獲僱主擔保的人。<br />\n將來持有臨時技術簽證的港人，亦在5年簽證完結時，有途徑申請永久居留權。<br />\n吸納最有前途人士<br />\n<br />\n政府會透過優才計劃（Global Talent）和商業創新及投資計劃（Business Innovation and Investment），吸納香港最有前途的人士。這兩項計劃均有永久居留權。<br />\n這些計劃會優先處理港人申請，並有一名優才計劃審核官員專門處理港人申請。<br />\n吸納生意<br />\n<br />\n政府會推出新措施，來吸引香港的出口商到澳洲。除了經濟誘利外，政府亦會向這些生意的香港骨幹成員，提供永久居留的途徑。政府特別針對目前計劃將總部撒出香港前往民主國家的企業。"},{"pid":"8b818fb452e0909c497367adc732acafe513bec1","tid":2099883,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e5026c067cb25e0f6e043d6ac376430be6f452","tid":2099883,"uid":362508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b818fb452e0909c497367adc732acafe513bec1","tid":2099883,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔收我會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3e84190ea780dde149d8783d62e7aaa2f0d333","tid":2099883,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e5026c067cb25e0f6e043d6ac376430be6f452","tid":2099883,"uid":362508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b818fb452e0909c497367adc732acafe513bec1","tid":2099883,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔收